product.longDescription:
This Spinner Underseater boasts the modern convenience of a USB port and the mobility of spinner wheels to move across all surfaces with ease.
• Fits under most airline seats
• Four, multi-directional spinner wheels for easy mobility
• Integrated charging port allows for easy access to personal portable chargers (personal batteries not included)
• Interior mesh organization pockets, laptop and tablet sleeve
• Exterior zippered pocket with organizational panel for quick stash and organization for smaller items
• Additional exterior pocket for quick stash items
• Smart sleeve on back allows bag to be placed over handle of most upright luggage pieces

*Under seat storage capacities and dimensions vary by airline – please check with your airline for more information.
• Weight: 5.6 lbs.

Body Dimensions: 15.0" x 13.0" x 8.0"
Overall Dimensions: 16.5" x 13.75" x 9.0"
